    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-05-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-05-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="526" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d526">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Uhl</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Terrell</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-05-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Five thirty received. Webber’s case, Brusa, should be searchingly
                            investigated. If death proves to have resulted from cruelty or neglect,
                            delinquent officials should be sternly dealt with. Report result of
                            investigation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Uhl</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
